        "item_mkzghj": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I take it with my current medications?",
            "content": "<p>Made from 100% natural botanicals. No known interactions with HRT, common medications or supplements. Phytoseed Labs is a natural food supplement and is generally suitable to take alongside your current medications.</p>"
          }
        },
        "166442457738b23caf-0": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Description",
            "content": "<p>Phytoseed Labs. is a powerful, clean supplement designed to support your immune system, gut health, and overall well-being.<br/><br/>Each softgel combines concentrated oregano oil extract with black seed oil (200 mg)—two clinically studied ingredients to support your body's natural defenses.<br/><br/>No fillers. No aftertaste.</p><p>Whether you’re looking to support your immune system, ease digestive discomfort, or maintain daily wellness—Phytoseed Labs was made for you.</p><p>This daily formula helps your body stay strong, balanced, and resilient—all from two powerful plants used for centuries and now informed by modern research.</p>"
          }
        },
        "166442457738b23caf-1": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Benefits",
            "content": "<p><strong>Less bloating by evening</strong> — no more planning outfits around your stomach</p><p>✦ <strong>More energy from the inside out</strong> — not the jittery kind, the kind that actually lasts</p><p>✦ <strong>Clearer head, better focus</strong> — the fog lifts, the sharpness comes back</p><p>✦ <strong>Calmer nights</strong> — fewer disruptions, more of the deep rest your body is asking for</p><p>✦ <strong>Feel like yourself again</strong> — not a younger version, just the real you</p>"
          }
        },
        "166442457738b23caf-2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Recommended use",
            "content": "<p>Take 1 softgel per day with food. Most women start noticing a difference within 2–4 weeks, with fuller results building over 4–6 weeks of consistent use — this isn't a quick fix, it's designed to work <em>with</em> your body over time. Do not exceed the recommended daily dose.</p><p>* Individual results may vary. Consult your healthcare provider before use if you are pregnant, nursing, taking medication, or have a medical condition.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_yRx3Yi": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Ingredients",
            "content": "<p>\"UK-Based Quality Control\"</p><p>Oil of Oregano (<em>Origanum vulgare</em>) — 6,000 mg (standardized to 80% carvacrol and 5% thymol)<br/>Black Seed Oil (<em>Nigella sativa</em>) — 200 mg</p><p>Other ingredients: Softgel shell (gelatin, glycerin, purified water). Contains no fillers, binders, artificial colors, or preservatives.</p><p>Free from: Gluten, dairy, soy, sugar, GMOs, artificial additives.</p>"
